{
  "bookId": "laozi-wangbi-wiki",
  "num": 52,
  "title": "第五十二章",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "天下有始，以為天下母。"
    },
    {
      "text": "既得其母，以知其子，既知其子，復守其母，沒身不殆。"
    },
    {
      "text": "塞其兌，閉其門，"
    },
    {
      "text": "終身不勤。"
    },
    {
      "text": "開其兌，濟其事，終身不救。"
    },
    {
      "text": "見小曰明，守柔曰強。"
    },
    {
      "text": "用其光，"
    },
    {
      "text": "復歸其明，"
    },
    {
      "text": "無遺身殃，是為習常。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "善始之則善養畜之矣，故天下有始則可以為天下母矣。(按此段注文原脫，據樓宇烈補。)",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 25
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "母，本也，子，末也。得本以知末，不舍本以逐末也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "兌，事欲之所由生；門，事欲之所由從也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "無事永逸，故終身不勤也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 13
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不閉其原而濟其事，故雖終身不救。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "為治之功不在大，見大不明，見小乃明。守强不强，守柔乃强也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "顯道以去民迷。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不明察也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "道之常也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
